thread.title: Sarah Hood

author: Sarah Hood
title: Sarah Hood
text: I needed a couple of small (25) batches of cards, and wanted to use a few different cover images for each set. Not such an easy thing to find on the internet, but something MOO.COM is able to accommodate, so I thought I'd give them a try. I'm absolutely blown away by the quality of the cards at the price, and they arrived barely a week after I ordered them (on standard delivery). I'll definitely be using MOO.COM for all future printing needs. Thank you!
